Machine Learning


 

 

Machine Learning

Version - 1.0

 

Machine Learning is an all in one bundled package that contains the sub-programs that were created and designed specifically for machine learning.


Features


- Consists of various programs which could be used for general purposes.

- No need to install any other libraries or tools apart from the default ones.

- User friendly and responsive UI.

System Requirements


CPU - Intel Core i3 or higher

RAM - 4 GB or higher

HDD - 1.5GB of disk space required

Mouse and keyboard are required

Directx9.0c or higher is required

.Net Framework 4.5.2 or higher
 

Microsoft Visual C++ 2005 - 2019 is required


Download




FAQ


1. What CPU architecture does Machine Learning support?

Answer

Machine Learning has support for both x86 and x64 bits CPU architecture, however it only works flawlessly on a 64 bit Windows operating system.


2. Why does the program 'Task 3' i.e 'Attendance System' work only on Windows 8 or higher versions of windows?

Answer

The reason could be related to the libraries of the program and the version of drivers of the camera or webcam followed by the version and structure of the windows operating system which causes or causing the program to crash.
